What are Local inner classes?
Local inner classes are those classes defined inside block or method.
-->Local inner classes are used to define specific required functionality for that method.
Local inner class's scope is limited to that method and is rarely used.

Can we access local variable of the wrapping method inside local inner class?
-->Yes, we can access final or non-final method inside local inner class but we can not modify them.

What access modifier can be used with local inner class?
-->Local inner is the local inner of the method, so it can not be public, private, protected.
It can only be final or abstract.


